Whisk together lime juice, rice vinegar, soy sauce and ginger in a small bowl. Pour in the oil in a thin stream, mixing until incorporated. Combine the BUSH'S BEST Black Beans, scallions and red peppers in a large bowl. Toss well with the dressing. Refrigerate, covered, until ready to serve. Just before serving, arrange lettuce on platter. Add mint, shrimp and peanuts to the salad and arrange on the lettuce.